Name: twitterframe
Version: 1.0.0
Summary: A basic command line application used in tandem with Twitter API to frame anything from Twitter into a Pandas DataFrame, or exported as a CSV.
Home-page: https://github.com/Ruwai/twitterframe
Author: Ruwai
